metadata.name: Ai-Jesus piece #1
metadata.description:
This series is a collaboration between artist & artificial intelligence image generator, Dall-E. Every word prompt contained the word Jesus to generate a digital ai image of Jesus. After the artist manipulates the Dall-E generated image in photoshop it is minted as a 1/1.

This series is simply a collection to visualize ai generated versions of Jesus. These images are in no way meant to offend, but to explore what the digital aesthetics of Jesus would materialize as.

We feel Easter is an appropriate day to let this project arise from the digital abyss of web3.
